# Basic Usage

Note that switches are usually used in conjunction with [form
fields](Material-FormField).

    import Material.Switch as Switch

    data Msg
        = Changed

    main =
        Switch.switch
            (Switch.config
                |> Switch.setChecked True
                |> Switch.setOnChange Changed
            )


